specification:
  - Substructures shared by most family events and attributes.
  - Wife
  - |
    A structure for storing information related to one partner in the context of a
    `FAMILY_EVENT`; in particular, the partner referenced in the
    `https://gedcom.io/terms/v7.1/FAM-WIFE` substructure of the
    `https://gedcom.io/terms/v7.1/record-FAM` superstructure of the `FAMILY_EVENT`.
    
    <div class="example">
    
    The following indicates that individual `@I2@` was 32 years old at the time of
    the marriage, without indicating an age for individual `@I1@`.
    
    ```gedcom
    0 @F1@ FAM
    1 HUSB @I1@
    1 WIFE @I2@
    1 MARR
    2 WIFE
    3 AGE 32y
    ```
    
    </div>

